Plot: Something is happening to me that I don't understand. I see things, feel things in a new way. I can do things normal people can't do. Powerful things. Magical things. It scares me. I never chose to learn witchcraft. But I'm starting to wonder if witchcraft is choosing me.
Characters: Robbie Gurevitch, Morgan Rowlands, Calhoun Blaire, Bree Warren, Raven Meltzer, Mary Grace Rowlands, Mary Kathleen Rowlands, Alyce Fernbrake, David Redfern, Sean Rowlands
